.container-fluid
  .col-md-6
      h3 Settings
      h4 Blur Images
      p.
          When browing sensitive material, you may want to blur the images displayed. This option
          allows you to blur images all the time, never, or blur them except when they are hovered over.
       .im-blur-controls
         .btn-group(role="group", data-toggle="buttons")
           label.btn.btn-default(class=(blur == "never") ? "active": "")
             input(type="radio", name="blur-options", value="never")
             | Never
           label.btn.btn-default(class=(blur == "hover") ? "active": "")
             input(type="radio", name="blur-options", value="hover")
             | Hover
           label.btn.btn-default(class=(blur == "always") ? "active": "")
             input(type="radio", name="blur-options", value="always")
             | Always
